.Dd April 28, 2026
.Dt TREE 1
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm tree
.Nd display one or more directory tree
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Nm
.Op Fl a
.Op Fl d
.Op Fl L Ar depth
.Op Ar path ...
.Op Ar another_path ...
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The Nm utility displays a tree representation of directories.
.Sh OPTIONS
.Bl -tag -width indent
.It Fl a
Show hidden files.
.It Fl d
Directories only.
.It Fl L Ar depth
Maximum display depth.
.El
EOF